HEADWORD: Strongly
<hw>Strong"ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a strong manner; so as to be
strong in action or in resistance; with strength; with great force;
forcibly; powerfully; firmly; vehemently; <as>as, a town
<ex>strongly</ex> fortified; he objected
<ex>strongly</ex>.</as></def>⟦br⟧
